    <item>
      <title>贝克休斯首席执行官预计美国钻井业务将疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/baker-hughes-ceo-expects-weakness-in-us-drilling-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝克休斯首席执行官 Lorenzo Simonelli 预计今年下半年美国钻井市场将疲软，但他表示全球能源需求正在上升。Simonelli 表示，还有机会为人工智能领域的科技公司提供动力。他正在接受“彭博监测”采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/baker-hughes-ceo-expects-weakness-in-us-drilling-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 12:44:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国贸易逆差扩大至 788 亿美元，创两年来最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/us-trade-deficit-widens-to-78-8-billion-largest-in-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受商品进口激增推动，以及企业在可能发生的码头工人罢工之前加大力度确保充足供应，美国贸易逆差在 7 月份扩大至两年来最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/us-trade-deficit-widens-to-78-8-billion-largest-in-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 12:31:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚法院正在考虑币安高管的保释申请</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/nigerian-court-weighs-binance-executive-s-application-for-bail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚一家法院将于 10 月 9 日对币安控股有限公司一名高管的保释申请作出判决，该高管已在该西非国家被关押六个多月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/nigerian-court-weighs-binance-executive-s-application-for-bail</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 12:03:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿联酋阿布扎比国家石油公司收购埃克森美孚德州氢气工厂 35% 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/abu-dhabi-s-adnoc-buys-35-stake-in-exxon-s-texas-hydrogen-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布扎比国家石油公司同意收购埃克森美孚公司位于德克萨斯州贝敦的氢气项目 35% 的股份，该项目一旦建成，很可能成为世界上最大的氢气项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/abu-dhabi-s-adnoc-buys-35-stake-in-exxon-s-texas-hydrogen-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求不足导致沃尔沃汽车下调电动汽车目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/volvo-car-walks-back-electric-push-after-disappointing-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔沃汽车公司放弃了本世纪末只销售全电动汽车的目标，由于需求减弱，该公司成为最新一家放弃电动汽车目标的汽车制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/volvo-car-walks-back-electric-push-after-disappointing-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:56:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦金属交易所 (LME) 采取措施推动市场改革，促进电子交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/lme-planning-measures-to-boost-trading-in-monthly-contracts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金属交易所（London Metal Exchange）正计划采取措施，促进其月度合约的电子交易，此举可能会减少其独特的三个月滚动合约的活动，该合约是全球金属行业的基准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/lme-planning-measures-to-boost-trading-in-monthly-contracts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球经济担忧导致欧洲股市科技股下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/european-stock-futures-drop-on-us-economy-fears-before-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对全球经济健康状况的担忧削弱了本周晚些时候美国关键就业数据公布前的市场人气，欧洲股市下跌。科技股下跌，追随英伟达公司隔夜下跌的脚步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/european-stock-futures-drop-on-us-economy-fears-before-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 05:46:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
